## PART 7 — HOW THIS CONNECTS TO GAME SETTINGS COMPATIBILITY ROW

When the user taps "Compatibility Layer" in the Game Settings → Compatibility panel:

1. Open a `ModalBottomSheet` showing installed versions only (fast, no network)
2. At the bottom of the sheet: "Manage versions →" button that navigates to the full Component screen for that source
3. Selecting a version calls `RuntimeManager.setActive(appId, release)` and updates the Compatibility row display

